race.comment: The $300,000 Group 3 Vo Rogue Plate for three-year-olds. NINJA (2) hasn't done much wrong to start the career with two wins and two placings from four starts with both those victories coming over this distance range. Will be better for that first-up hit-out at Doomben and looks the one they all have to run down. BIG PAPA (4) looked good winning at Hawkesbury two back before just running into a couple better at Randwick last time out. Strips fitter third-up from the spell and can make his presence felt. O' OLE (6) is improving with racing this campaign and should be able to sit up on speed from gate five. Will give backers a sight. METAL MAN (5) is one from one around this circuit and looks a must for the multiples. DAMIEN (1) best of the rest in a competitive affair.
